    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挥舞你的剑，重温打斗游戏的黄金时代！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Blades &amp; Battles》融合了《金斧》等经典游戏的精神与2.5D风格化的3D战斗强度。探索受亚瑟王传说启发的幻想世界，在决定圆桌骑士命运的史诗级战斗中奋勇作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/e267444230d2789e207fe433baa1e4d1.poster.avif?t=1770650768\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/e267444230d2789e207fe433baa1e4d1.webm?t=1770650768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演亚瑟或兰斯洛特，他们各具独特的技能、不同的战斗风格和毁灭性的特殊攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/a3c7f878965b3231970c762d8b75bc58.poster.avif?t=1770650768\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/a3c7f878965b3231970c762d8b75bc58.webm?t=1770650768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/a3c7f878965b3231970c762d8b75bc58.mp4?t=1770650768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本地合作战斗中对抗成群的敌人，以现代、电影般的、充满动作的呈现方式重温街机游戏的辉煌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/a2e747feba5b80013f3f86680b526272.poster.avif?t=1770650768\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/a2e747feba5b80013f3f86680b526272.webm?t=1770650768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284260/extras/a2e747feba5b80013f3f86680b526272.mp4?t=1770650768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位传奇英雄：扮演亚瑟或兰斯洛特，他们各具独特的武器和招式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地合作：在合作战役模式中与好友并肩作战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.5D 风格化视觉效果：采用像素滤镜的 3D 艺术风格，融合新旧元素。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典打斗游戏新演绎：直接动作、连击、魔法和巨型BOSS。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神话故事：探索圆桌骑士团成立前的传奇冒险。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借精美的3D场景和复古像素滤镜，《刀锋与战役》是对90年代经典游戏的致敬之作，为新一代骑士和独立游戏爱好者重新打造。</p>",
